Digital Medicine Center

Respecting user privacy and data protection is our commitment at the Digital Medicine Center. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, protect, and share your personal data. Please read the following content to understand our measures to protect your privacy.

Data Collection
We collect your personal data provided while using our services, including but not limited to: name, email address, contact number, usage records, etc. We will not collect more personal data than necessary unless we have obtained your consent.

Data Usage
We use your personal data to provide, maintain, improve, and develop our services. We will not use your personal data for any other purposes unless we have obtained your explicit consent.

Data Reference
We may use your personal data for research and development purposes to improve our services. If you consent to our use of your personal data, we will anonymize it before referencing to protect your privacy. If you do not consent to our use of your personal data, we will respect your choice and will not use it.

Data Protection
We take appropriate security measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access, use, disclosure, or destruction. We regularly review and update our security measures to ensure the best protection of your personal data.

Data Sharing
We will not share your personal data with any third party unless we have obtained your explicit consent or are required by law. If we need to share your personal data with a third party, we will notify you in advance and obtain your consent.

Privacy Policy Updates
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy at any time. If there are any updates, we will notify you by posting a notice on our website or through other appropriate means. If you continue to use our services, you are deemed to have accepted the updated Privacy Policy.

Contact Us
If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy or your personal data, please contact us at:

Digital Medicine Center
https://dmc.nycu.edu.tw/

Thank you for your attention to our Privacy Policy. We will continue to strive to provide you with the best privacy protection.
